  "detailed_description": "Fight & scavenge, gather powerups to survive, and don't waste a step, for with every wasted moment, a terrifying beast draws closer, ready to reap your soul. Go alone or with a buddy as you roadtrip across a dangerous, randomly-generated world.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A THRILLING, DIFFICULT, ROGUELITE, ROADTRIP ADVENTURE</h2>Death's Toll takes you on a randomly-generated journey across a dangerous world filled with colorful characters. The game heavily focuses on the constant threat presented by the always-following beast. Sleep will be limited, supplies will need to be gathered and used sparingly, and along the way, expect to meet a plethora of really strange NPC's. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/17114c9519b5e49871035c9a96aef46b.poster.avif?t=1718686932\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/17114c9519b5e49871035c9a96aef46b.webm?t=1718686932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/17114c9519b5e49871035c9a96aef46b.mp4?t=1718686932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOUR PATH IS YOUR OWN</h2>Every adventure begins with a randomly generated map for you to traverse through. Pick which spots you want to visit and learn what may await behind each icon!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/41a98b080ac48cd48a6475b6cd83a975.poster.avif?t=1718686932\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/41a98b080ac48cd48a6475b6cd83a975.webm?t=1718686932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/41a98b080ac48cd48a6475b6cd83a975.mp4?t=1718686932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT, SCAVENGE, AND KEEP MOVING</h2>A variety of enemies stand in your path, just as you have a variety of classes to choose from. Pick your fighting style and use it to push forward, picking up food, drinks, and powerups along the way!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/5405d32f919dc50ce9fe0c04eadf669f.poster.avif?t=1718686932\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/5405d32f919dc50ce9fe0c04eadf669f.webm?t=1718686932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/5405d32f919dc50ce9fe0c04eadf669f.mp4?t=1718686932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAKE TOUGH CHOICES</h2>Every good adventure has some roadblocks- some a little dumber than others... <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/f24426bdf96681989dabcd674b937a21.poster.avif?t=1718686932\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/f24426bdf96681989dabcd674b937a21.webm?t=1718686932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/f24426bdf96681989dabcd674b937a21.mp4?t=1718686932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MEET TOTAL WEIRDOS</h2>There's no shortage of odd characters to meet... NPC's can be found in abundance. Your own character gets a personality of your choosing! From Hero to Vigilante, Wild Card to Menace, there's hundreds of unique lines to find.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/1f3f66c069ead9b019a3098565245a67.poster.avif?t=1718686932\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/1f3f66c069ead9b019a3098565245a67.webm?t=1718686932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/1f3f66c069ead9b019a3098565245a67.mp4?t=1718686932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VENDING MACHINE</h2>vending machine<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/181760d51e5823de069e7088d27a374c.poster.avif?t=1718686932\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/181760d51e5823de069e7088d27a374c.webm?t=1718686932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404070/extras/181760d51e5823de069e7088d27a374c.mp4?t=1718686932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br>And hey buddy... we got a LOT more vending machines where that came from.",
